first, you need to clone this repo
```bash
yum install -y git
git clone https://github.com/mod96/Mmumshad-CKA.git
```
or,
```bash
apt-get install -y git
git clone https://github.com/mod96/Mmumshad-CKA.git
```
by running `.bash` file, you'll install `docker`, `kubelet`, `kubeadm`, `kubectl`, `kubernetes-cni`